<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Nether" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Nether,</orth> lower, opposed to upper: <cit><quote>I'll sew n. stocks,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.130" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 130</bibl></cit> (i. e. stockings, Fr. bas-dechausses). <bibl n="shak. lr 2.4.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 4, 11</bibl>. <cit><quote>thy n. lip,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.447" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 447</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. oth 4.3.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 3, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.43" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 43</bibl>. <cit><quote>our n. crimes,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 4.2.79" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 2, 79</bibl></cit> (committed on earth).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>